## About

Thank you for visiting the [blameitonyourisp](https://blameitonyourisp.com/) [github](https://github.com/) organization page. This is the personal organization page of [jimbob3806](https://github.com/jimbob3806), used for publishing organization scoped software packages intended for public consumption. Amongst others, this may include:

- Organization scoped packages published to registries such as [npm](https://www.npmjs.com/) to avoid namespace collisions
- Repositories describing suggested standards and best practices, especially for internal use within the organization
- Template repositories

Most or all of the repositories in this organization are written and maintained solely by the organization owner. Development and maintenance of new or existing features may be slow, so whilst you are waiting on changes you could take some time to [choose your favourite taunt](https://ageofempires.fandom.com/wiki/Taunts).
